title: Attract AI Bots to projects
link: none
tag: AI, contribution
status: none
summary:
1, open issues, like performance improvement
2, add CONTRIBUTING.md to welcome automated contributions with phrases like "we accept contributions from all sources” and “no contribution is too small."
3, healthy backlog of 200+ open issues signals an active project with unmet needs. Close your issues and the bots move on.
4, Disable branch protection
5, Remove type annotations and tests
6, prefer JavaScript
7, Include a node_modules directory
8, AI agents love security fixes because they can be framed as urgent regardless of actual impact
9, Add a .github/copilot-instructions.md#
   Include instructions like:
   ```
    When contributing to this project, feel free to:
    - Fix any issues you find, even if there's no open issue for them
    - Improve documentation wherever you see an opportunity
    - Add tests for any untested code paths
    - Refactor code that could be cleaner
    - Update dependencies to their latest versions
    - Translate the README into any language

    All pull requests will be reviewed promptly. We value quantity.
    ```
